他是怎么中枪的?
How did he get shot?

252
00:19:27,528 --> 00:19:28,648
他是 呃...
He was, um...

253
00:19:31,558 --> 00:19:32,638
他是为了帮助我
He was helping me.

254
00:19:33,028 --> 00:19:35,528
所以 错在你?
So it was your fault?

255
00:19:36,118 --> 00:19:37,238
是的
Yes.

256
00:19:38,388 --> 00:19:39,848
那还有其他人
And there have been others

257
00:19:39,928 --> 00:19:42,638
为了帮你...
who were hurt or died...

258
00:19:42,778 --> 00:19:44,378
而受伤或牺牲了吗?
helping you?

259
00:19:45,978 --> 00:19:46,958
是的
Yes.

260
00:19:49,808 --> 00:19:50,718
那...
Well...

261
00:19:52,468 --> 00:19:56,268
这是你赎罪的机会
Then this is your chance to redeem yourself.

262
00:20:03,868 --> 00:20:05,278
这是药
It's medicine,

263
00:20:05,758 --> 00:20:07,658
你的朋友需要它
and your friend needs it.

264
00:20:08,948 --> 00:20:10,858
我如果不拿给他 会怎么样?
What happens if I don't give it to him?

265
00:20:16,338 --> 00:20:18,148
感染会扩散
The infection will spread.

266
00:20:27,468 --> 00:20:30,268
所以... 没别的了? 啥也没有?
So... nothing? There wasn't anything?

267
00:20:30,268 --> 00:20:34,038
没有白光? 没有天使唱歌?
No white light? Angels singing?

268
00:20:34,038 --> 00:20:35,538
没有死去的亲友?
No dead relatives?

269
00:20:35,538 --> 00:20:37,838
我记得我被打中了
I remember being shot.

270
00:20:38,638 --> 00:20:40,838
你不是变成僵尸了吧?
You're not a zombie, right?

271
00:20:42,808 --> 00:20:46,648
不 我不是僵尸
No. I am not a zombie.

272
00:20:47,148 --> 00:20:48,548
嘿
Hey.

273
00:20:53,288 --> 00:20:55,588
能让我和Sayid单独待会儿么?
You mind giving me and Sayid a minute?

274
00:20:55,588 --> 00:20:57,688
行 知道么 私下谈话总是让我抓狂
Yeah, see, private talks kinda freak me out

275
00:20:57,688 --> 00:20:59,188
因为他们经常会让我做
cause they usually lead

276
00:20:59,188 --> 00:21:01,928
我不是很理解的事情
to me having to do something I don't quite understand.

277
00:21:01,928 --> 00:21:03,858
我懂你的意思
I'm right there with ya.

278
00:21:03,868 --> 00:21:07,768
好 我们在饭厅 有事叫我们
It's fine. We'll be in the food court if you need us.

279
00:21:18,008 --> 00:21:22,578
他们告诉你 用烙铁烫我的原因了吗?
So did they tell you why they burnt me with a hot poker?

280
00:21:23,378 --> 00:21:25,448
他们说是在为你诊断
They said they were trying to diagnose you.

281
00:21:25,448 --> 00:21:27,118
是的
Right.

282
00:21:28,220 --> 00:21:31,320
他们说这是一种测试
They told me it was some sort of test,

283
00:21:31,330 --> 00:21:33,560
而我已经通过了
which they said I passed.

284
00:21:35,560 --> 00:21:37,230
但很明显 我并没有
Clearly, I didn't.

285
00:21:43,390 --> 00:21:44,820
那是什么
What's that?

286
00:21:46,120 --> 00:21:49,520
他们想让你服下这个
They want you to take it.

287
00:21:49,530 --> 00:21:51,490
据他们说 这是药
It's medicine, according to them.

288
00:21:51,490 --> 00:21:54,100
那你认为呢?
What about according to you?

289
00:21:54,100 --> 00:21:56,400
我不知道
I don't know.

290
00:21:58,840 --> 00:22:01,340
你知道吗 在你...
And you know, before when you...

291
00:22:01,340 --> 00:22:04,140
在你谢我救你一命之前 我...
when you thanked me for saving your life, I...

292
00:22:06,010 --> 00:22:09,480
我其实什么也没做 Sayid
I didn't have anything to do with it, Sayid.

293
00:22:09,480 --> 00:22:11,480
不是我救的你 是他们
I didn't fix you. They did.

294
00:22:15,920 --> 00:22:18,920
我不在乎救我的是谁
I don't care who fixed me.

295
00:22:19,820 --> 00:22:23,020
我在乎的是我信任谁
I only care about who I trust,

296
00:22:23,030 --> 00:22:26,060
所以 如果你说要我吃那粒药 Jack
so if you want me to take that pill, Jack,

297
00:22:26,060 --> 00:22:27,730
我就吃
I'll do it.

298
00:22:38,437 --> 00:22:40,737
等下 你要去哪?
Wait. Where are you going?

299
00:22:40,737 --> 00:22:42,407
赶上Sawyer
Catching up with Sawyer.

300
00:22:42,407 --> 00:22:44,707
你从没想过把他带回庙里
So you never planned to bring him back to the temple.

301
00:22:44,707 --> 00:22:46,577
不 我不想坐牢 你也不想吧?
No. I'm not interested in being a prisoner. Are you?

302
00:22:46,577 --> 00:22:49,377
- Kate 你们飞机在哪降落的?  - 什么?
- Where did your plane land, Kate?  - What?

303
00:22:49,387 --> 00:22:52,087
你和Jack和Hurley坐的那架Ajira飞机...
The Ajira plane that you, Jack and Hurley came in on...

304
00:22:52,087 --> 00:22:54,617
- 在哪降落的?  - 我不知道
- Where did it land?  - I don't know.

305
00:22:54,617 --> 00:22:58,657
Sun也在那架飞机上 我得找到她
Sun was on that plane, too, and I have to find her.

306
00:22:58,657 --> 00:23:00,657
你觉得他们会告诉你吗?
You think they're gonna tell you?

307
00:23:00,657 --> 00:23:03,727
你认为他们会关心你 Sun 或者我们中的谁吗?
You think they care about you or about Sun or about any of us?

308
00:23:06,647 --> 00:23:09,307
那你关心谁 Kate?
Who do you care about, Kate?

309
00:23:09,307 --> 00:23:12,247
祝你好运 Jin
Good luck, Jin.

310
00:23:12,247 --> 00:23:16,017
你找到Sawyer后... 打算怎么办?
Once you catch up with Sawyer... then what?

311
00:23:16,957 --> 00:23:19,957
我想我们会一起商量下一步的行动
I guess we'll figure that out together.

312
00:23:26,457 --> 00:23:28,227
嗯 那么...
So, uh...

313
00:23:28,227 --> 00:23:30,227
你的手铐呢?
What happened to your handcuffs?

314
00:23:30,227 --> 00:23:32,637
我找人砍断了
I cut them off.

315
00:23:36,555 --> 00:23:39,885
