I bet they're a really nice couple.

317
00:23:47,535 --> 00:23:49,465
怎么了?
What?

318
00:23:49,465 --> 00:23:51,435
我什么都没说啊
I didn't say anything.

319
00:23:51,435 --> 00:23:55,775
