哦 天哪
Oh, my god.

330
00:24:47,685 --> 00:24:50,595
真抱歉
I'm so so sorry.

331
00:24:50,595 --> 00:24:53,365
呃...
Um...

332
00:24:54,315 --> 00:24:57,315
