But...

336
00:25:10,890 --> 00:25:13,460
我一个人 真的负担不了
I can't do it alone.

337
00:25:13,460 --> 00:25:14,760
对不起
I'm sorry.

338
00:25:14,760 --> 00:25:18,130
是 我知道 我早该打电话告诉你的
Look, I know I should've called you

339
00:25:18,130 --> 00:25:19,800
所以 呃 那么...
So, uh, what...

340
00:25:19,800 --> 00:25:22,230
你... 你... 你就这样反悔了?
Y... y... you just changed your mind?

341
00:25:22,240 --> 00:25:24,370
瞧 我... 我的生活已经...
Look, my... my life is just...

342
00:25:24,370 --> 00:25:26,370
已经一团糟了
a little bit complicated.

343
00:25:26,370 --> 00:25:29,510
她大老远从澳大利亚跑来 可你却连电话都不打一个?
She came all the way from Australia, and you don't call?

344
00:25:29,510 --> 00:25:30,740
哦 我的天哪
Oh, my god.

345
00:25:32,980 --> 00:25:34,650
你还好吗?
Are you Ok?

346
00:25:34,650 --> 00:25:37,580
啊! 我要生了!
Aah! It's coming!

347
00:27:22,920 --> 00:27:24,420
谁在那儿?
Who's there?

348
00:27:25,890 --> 00:27:27,590
马上出来
Better come out now

349
00:27:27,590 --> 00:27:30,220
否则 我就开枪了
or so help me, I'm just gonna start shooting.

350
00:27:34,360 --> 00:27:36,530
你来这干什么?
What the hell are you doing here?

351
00:27:38,530 --> 00:27:40,670
我很担心你
I was worried about you.

352
00:28:13,020 --> 00:28:14,050
她是怎么了?
What's happening?

353
00:28:14,250 --> 00:28:17,920
- 我... 我想我已经宫缩了  - 什么时候开始的?
- I... I think I'm having contractions.  -  When did they start?

354
00:28:17,920 --> 00:28:20,020
